Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:33.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen has abducted Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:34.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:37.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and his friends\Nhave marched into Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:41.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They break into Las Noches,\Nthe Arrancars’ hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,During his battle\Nwith Gantenbainne,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:50.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado awakens the power\Nthat had been resting within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:53.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nnoitora, one of the Espada,\Nsuddenly appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:56.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado is powerless before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:01:59.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:02.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.\NYou really are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chad was defeated?!\NThat's impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We vowed that\Nwe'd come back alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:28.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I'd be angry that they were\Nfoolish enough to come to Hueco Mundo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing the limits\Nof their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:40.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Rukia is fighting Aaroniero.\NShe too, was facing danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My ability is Glotoneria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I devour dead Hollows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:58.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and make their abilities\Nand Spiritual Pressure my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:04.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power I received\Nwhen I devoured Metastacia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:07.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when he came back\Nin Kaien Shiba's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:10.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This body is Kaien Shiba's!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:13.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In his body,\Nall of his experiences…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In his brain,\Nall of his memories…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:17.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:24.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just read his memories\Nand experiences and acted accordingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:33.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you\Nan Espada's sword release.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Devour! Glotoneria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice expression.\NYou're scared, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Become even more terrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:17.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of all\Nthe Hollows I have devoured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:23.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect an Espada's sword release\Nto be like that of a regular Arrancar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Glotoneria can display
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:31.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all the powers of the Hollows\NI have eaten at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:39.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So far, I've eaten 33,650 Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:49.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be just like fighting an army of\Nmore than 30,000 Hollows by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Kaien…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:16.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Kaien…\NI'm very sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems this is the end for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:31.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your body has fallen into the hands\Nof a Hollow because I killed you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:41.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I killed you back then\Nin order to save myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even so…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry about that,\Nit must have been harsh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to you…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:55.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can leave my heart here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:06:01.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got Sir Kaien's body\Nback from the enemy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:07.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the one thing that\NI told myself had saved him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it seems even that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was also a mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:23.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have the strength left\Nto swing my sword anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:23.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have any strength left{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:32.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to swing my sword\Nat your body, Sir Kaien.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye Sir Kaien.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good…bye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:05.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kuchiki… Kuchiki…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing, Sir Kaien?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't respond when\NI call you or nudge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I had gotten\Na crick in my neck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A crick in your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you sleep-walking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez… Stop daydreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get\Nleft behind, Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:43.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind hits my forehead…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The forest opens out\Nonto our path ahead…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The smell of the grass…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sunshine…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:56.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The birds chirping…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:19.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember…this landscape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Each tree…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:35.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This combined feeling\Nof anxiety, excitement, and warmth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:40.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is West Rukon District,\NArea 3, North end, Mt. Koifushi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:50.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the place where\NSir Kaien first trained me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:55.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the Lieutenant, Kaien Shiba!\NNice to meet ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Umm… Yes, sir”?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with that greeting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Lieutenant\Njust introduced himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to\Nstate your name and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Pleased to meet you too, sir,”\Nright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s your name, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:21.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m R-Rukia Kuchiki, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:23.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pleased to meet you too, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:26.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:33.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ordinary greeting,\Nan ordinary yelling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:36.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an ordinary\Nsubordinate-superior relationship…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you to Squad 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain isn’t\Nin the best of health,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I’m pretty much\Nin charge of things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:49.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wouldn’t mind if you sometimes\Ncall me “Captain Kaien” by mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:58.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that ordinariness was,\Nwithout doubt,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just what I was seeking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not finished yet, Kuchiki!\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One more time, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A bird flies…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:19.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm distracted by\Nthe bird for a moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Kaien deflects my sword\NFrom the bottom left{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as I make my second strike.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's odd because I was\Ncaught up in the moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:47.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to eat, huh? All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're extremely self-asserting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:52.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like that, Sir Kaien!\NThat was…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:07.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir Kaien! Don't toss a sword\Nwhen it's unsheathed! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:09.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:18.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time, there was one thing\NI was worried about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:25.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, the entrance ceremony\Nwent smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What Seat are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…well…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:39.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With my abilities, I’m afraid I couldn’t\Nget an officer’s seat upon entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:40.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:56.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never had a gift\Nfor sword-fighting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dig your claws into\Nthe wall of sinless dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 33: Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:15.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My kido received good grades{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when I was at\Nthe Soul Reaper Academy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in the Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was average.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:35.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I really be here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is my purpose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:51.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:53.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To fight and defend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:57.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Defend what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Defend what”?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All sorts of things all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like\Na rather crude answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give me\Na slightly clearer answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A clearer answer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:21.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki, have you heard\Nour captain's theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:22.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:28.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two types of battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:35.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are battles to defend lives\Nand battles to defend people's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:39.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Captain Ukitake's theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:50.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think that, in the end,\Nhe's telling us to defend the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's so melodramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm being serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:05.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think that heart exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:11.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:17.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart is probably here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:34.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When we come into\Ncontact with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:42.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a heart is created between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:45.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart isn't within our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:52.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart is created when\Nwe think about something or someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:15:00.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the only person in the world,\NI wouldn't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:04.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That’s exactly what\NSir Kaien said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:10.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be here\Nfrom the bottom of your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then your heart is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:18.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If your heart is here,\Nthen that is your reason to be here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kuchiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:30.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When you fight from here on,\Nthere is one thing that you mustn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To die alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bodies are made of souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we die, our bodies will\Nsomeday turn to dust
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:45.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and become the reishi\Nthat makes up Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But where do our hearts go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:54.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hearts go to our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They go to our friends…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:04.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they go to our friends,\Nour hearts can live on within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:10.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't die alone, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that, Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:39.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kuchiki…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:43.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our hearts go to our friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful. No…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps I should\Ncall you unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:06.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long you hold on,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:10.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't change the fact\Nthat you cannot kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:22.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have the strength\Nto hold your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you remembered,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:38.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but what do you plan to do\Nwith a broken sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:49.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sanomai…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirafune.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:05.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:10.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered where my heart is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:15.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, you have\NSir Kaien's body within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:21.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sir Kaien is not in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:28.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am holding onto Sir Kaien's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Espada!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:09.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts!\NHelp me, Lord Aizen! Lord Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:15.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that if I stayed with you,\Nyou'd free me from all suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:20.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:21.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:23.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:30.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no…no…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:40.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't agree…with…this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't die…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:18.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't die, Kuchiki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:26.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't ever die alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know loneliness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The loneliness of\Nbeing a prisoner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:02.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know happiness. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:07.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The happiness of seeing\Nmy friends coming to save me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:14.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:22.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I know the terror of seeing\Na friend become injured and fall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry, Inoue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:37.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:23.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Nnoitora, the other day,\Nyou stuck your finger into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:23.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:28.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's how I inspect\Nthe Spiritual Pressure within Las Noches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:30.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:31.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:32.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Let's go, Tesla.\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:36.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:38.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NWe don't have any more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:41.78,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL REAPER WOMEN'S ASSOCIATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:41.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We've used up all of\N	our funds for this quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:45.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You all wasted our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:47.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Chairman,\Nyou used up most of our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:51.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, in order to\Ngather some quick funds,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to take pictures\Nof famous people and sell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:54.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the World of the Living,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.84,0:23:58.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,professional photographers known as\Npaparazzi make big money doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:23:59.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be targeting…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:01.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars of the Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:02.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– What?!\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:04.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!